main event: Multiple unidentified flying objects were observed in West Palm Beach, Florida on 3rd October. The objects varied in shape, size, and color, and were seen moving in different directions before disappearing at the horizon.
interesting points: Three square objects and four round objects of varying sizes and colors were observed in the sky.
The objects were witnessed for several seconds, moving in different directions and then disappearing at the horizon.
The observation was made by a civilian, specifically an interior decorator from Palm Beach, Florida.
The weather during the sighting was described as partly cloudy, warm, and humid.
There were no conclusive explanations provided, and the conclusion of the sighting was labeled as unknown.
